 class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ryi1665703135669.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ryi1665703135669.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ryi1665703135669.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ryi1665703135669\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__upaddocc_406784\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Create an empty occurrence of an entity.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__topic_d122744e1_d122745e1_d122746e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ryi1665703135669_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__codeblock_xw5_kh2_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">long upaddocc (unsigned char*Entity, longOccnum);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__topic_d86862e1_d86863e1_d86864e1_d86865e1_d86866e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d255355e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__parml_dj5_mh2_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Name of the entity. You can specify zero or an empty string to denote the current\n                  entity</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Occnum</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">sequence number of the new occurrence. Specify -1 to append a new occurrence at\n                  the end of the current hitlist, or zero to insert the occurrence before the\n                  current occurrence.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__topic_d86867e1_d86868e1_d86869e1_d86870e1_d86871e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d255355e90\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__table_d14942e1_d14943e1_d14944e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values Returned by upaddocc</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__table_d14942e1_d14943e1_d14944e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__table_d14942e1_d14943e1_d14944e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ryi1665703135669__table_d14942e1_d14943e1_d14944e1__entry__1\">&gt;0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ryi1665703135669__table_d14942e1_d14943e1_d14944e1__entry__2\">The sequence number of the newly created\n                        occurrence.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ryi1665703135669__table_d14942e1_d14943e1_d14944e1__entry__1\">-1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ryi1665703135669__table_d14942e1_d14943e1_d14944e1__entry__2\">The occurrence could not be created. Most\n                        likely causes: <var class=\"keyword varname\">Occnum</var> is out of range, or\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> does not exist, or is not painted on the\n                        component.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__topic_d86872e1_d86873e1_d86874e1_d86875e1_d86876e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d255355e148\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__topic_d86877e1_d86878e1_d86879e1_d86880e1_d86881e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d255355e161\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__p_d122771e1_d122772e1_d122773e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">upaddocc</code> creates an occurrence of\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> with sequence number <var class=\"keyword varname\">Occnum</var>. The\n            argument <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> contains the name of the entity in which the\n            occurrence will be created. Specify zero or an empty string to denote the current\n            entity.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__p_d122774e1_d122775e1_d122776e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">upaddocc</code> is equivalent to the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">creocc</span> ProcScript\n            statement, where you can find more information about the rules for creating\n            occurrences.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104ryi1665703135669_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"ryi1665703135669__codeblock_lcc_vh2_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\nEXPORT void ADDOCC ()\n{\nupaddocc(0, -1); /* Append occurrence to hitlist of current entity */\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/crd1665703135753.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>updelocc</a><p>Remove an occurrence of the specified entity from the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qem1665703135824.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>updisocc</a><p>Discard one or more occurrences of the specified entity from the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hor1665703135893.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>upsetocc</a><p>Make the specified occurrence current.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531845\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531845\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "upaddocc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Create an empty occurrence of an entity. Explain this code long upaddocc (unsigned char*Entity, longOccnum); Copy Parameters Entity Name of the entity. You can specify zero or an empty string to denote the current entity Occnum sequence number of the new occurrence. Specify -1 to append a new occurrence at the end of the current hitlist, or zero to insert the occurrence before the current occurrence. Return Values Table 1. Values Returned by upaddocc Value Meaning >0 The sequence number of the newly created occurrence. -1 The occurrence could not be created. Most likely causes: Occnum is out of range, or Entity does not exist, or is not painted on the component. Use Library: yrtl Description upaddocc creates an occurrence of Entity with sequence number Occnum . The argument Entity contains the name of the entity in which the occurrence will be created. Specify zero or an empty string to denote the current entity. upaddocc is equivalent to the creocc ProcScript statement, where you can find more information about the rules for creating occurrences. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> EXPORT void ADDOCC () { upaddocc(0, -1); /* Append occurrence to hitlist of current entity */ } Copy Related Links updelocc Remove an occurrence of the specified entity from the hitlist. updisocc Discard one or more occurrences of the specified entity from the hitlist. upsetocc Make the specified occurrence current. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}